text: Coro TV is a Venezuelan community television channel. It was created in July 2004 and can be seen in the community of Santa Ana de Coro in the Miranda Municipality of the Falcón State of Venezuela on UHF channel 68. Victor Gonzalez is the legal representative of the foundation that owns this channel.
